---
title: Herby Beef Rump & Winter Veggie Couscous with Slivered Almonds & Dill-Pasley Mayo
description: There’s a touch of summer and winter tonight, because why can’t we have both warm and cool at the same time? Cosy up with
a roast veggie couscous, those oven roasted flavours will delight your tastebuds. Cool off with herby beef and a dill and parsley
mayo.

